Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.53,0:13:38.70,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}兄貴[あにき, アニキ]:elder brother|one's senior|older man, 言いつける[いいつける]:to tell (to do)|to tell on (someone)|to often say, 気[き]:spirit|nature|motivation||, 気[げ]:seeming/giving the appearance of/giving one the feeling of
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.53,0:13:38.70,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,〈お前なぁ 何でも兄貴に\N言いつける気か？〉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.62,0:13:43.45,Ragtime,,0,0,0,,Yoshito's dad appears\Nin nine dramas every week.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.74,0:13:43.58,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}ゴールデン:golden, ドラマ:drama
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.74,0:13:43.58,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,ヨシトのオヤジさん\Nゴールデンのドラマに出てるんだぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.45,0:13:45.79,Ragtime,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I heard that from Maho.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.70,0:13:45.66,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}真帆[まほ]:spread-out sail/full sail/(sailing) downwind
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.70,0:13:45.66,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,ああ… 真帆から聞いたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.79,0:13:47.04,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,おい ヨシト
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.79,0:13:50.32,Ragtime,,0,0,0,,Hey, Yoshito! This guy sang at\NDying Breed's secret live performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.16,0:13:50.71,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}シークレット:secret, ライブ:live (esp. concert, show, etc.)/live performance, 歌う[うたう]:to sing|to sing (one's praises in a poem, etc.)/to compose a poem
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.16,0:13:50.71,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,こいつ ダイブリの\Nシークレットライブで歌ったんだぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.12,0:13:52.75,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,（ヨシト）ふ～ん
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.96,0:13:56.56,Ragtime,,0,0,0,,You know...My dad brought\Nan actress to my house last day...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.13,0:13:57.09,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}女優[じょゆう]:actress, 連れる[つれる]:to lead/to take (a person)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.13,0:13:57.09,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,〈この前さぁ オヤジのヤツ\N女優連れてきてさ〉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.97,0:14:00.10,Ragtime,,0,0,0,,-Who was it?\N-Guess who...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.05,0:13:59.51,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}友人[ゆうじん]:friend, 英語[えいご]:English (language)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.05,0:13:59.51,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,（友人：英語）〈誰だよ それ？〉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.20,0:14:24.95,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}どういう:somehow/how/in what way, 意味[いみ]:meaning/significance
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.20,0:14:24.95,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,（コユキ）あれは\Nどういう意味だったんだろう…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.33,0:14:24.95,Ragtime,,0,0,0,,I wonder what that was all about...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.84,0:14:42.76,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,（斎藤(さいとう)）何だって!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.94,0:14:42.45,Ragtime,,0,0,0,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.45,0:14:46.28,Ragtime,,0,0,0,,You mean we can't enter\Nthe singing contest this year?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.84,0:14:44.22,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}今年[ことし, こんねん]:this year, 歌謡[かよう]:song/ballad, コンテスト:contest
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.84,0:14:44.22,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,（斎藤）それじゃ 今年の\N歌謡コンテストには—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.34,0:14:46.26,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}参加[さんか]:participation
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.34,0:14:46.26,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,参加できないって言うのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.28,0:14:48.62,Ragtime,,0,0,0,,What do you mean,\Nthe Neighborhood Board Chair is mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.39,0:14:48.77,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}町内会[ちょうないかい]:neighborhood association/neighbourhood association, 長[たけ, たき]:height|length (esp. of clothing)|all (one has)|, 長[ちょう]:head|merit|superiority|, 怒る[おこる, いかる]:to get angry|to tell someone off|to be angular, そいつ:he/she|that
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.39,0:14:48.77,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,町内会長が怒ってる？\N誰だそいつはー！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.62,0:14:52.61,Ragtime,,0,0,0,,We've been practicing like crazy every day.\NShut up, will you? You nitwit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.85,0:14:53.02,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}連日[れんじつ]:day after day/every day, 猛練習[もうれんしゅう]:hard training, いい加減にしろ[いいかげんにしろ]:that's enough!/cut it out!/get a life!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.85,0:14:53.02,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,連日猛練習してんだぞ\Nいい加減にしろ このバカチンが！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.46,0:14:57.79,Ragtime,,0,0,0,,What's this all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.52,0:14:58.32,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}どういう:somehow/how/in what way
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.52,0:14:58.32,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,どういうことなんだよ！\Nなあ こらー！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.36,0:14:58.78,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}アハハ:a-ha-ha (laughing loudly)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.36,0:14:58.78,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,あ… アハハ…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.15,0:15:22.99,Ragtime,,0,0,0,,Long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.30,0:15:22.84,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}久しぶり[ひさしぶり]:a long time (since the last time)/it's been a while (since I last saw, mailed, etc., you)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.30,0:15:22.84,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,（泉(いずみ)）久しぶりだね
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.97,0:15:24.30,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}久しぶり[ひさしぶり]:a long time (since the last time)/it's been a while (since I last saw, mailed, etc., you)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.97,0:15:24.30,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,久しぶり…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.99,0:15:24.66,Ragtime,,0,0,0,,Nice to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.66,0:15:28.28,Ragtime,,0,0,0,,I was in the neighborhood,\Nso I decided to stop by.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.72,0:15:27.85,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}近く[ちかく]:near|nearly (e.g. "it took nearly one year")|shortly, 寄る[よる]:to approach|to gather (in one place)|to stop by (while on one's way to another place)||
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.72,0:15:27.85,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,（泉）ちょっと近くに来たからさ\N寄ってみたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.33,0:15:30.42,Ragtime,,0,0,0,,You've been well?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.47,0:15:30.31,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}元気[げんき]:lively/full of spirit|healthy
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.47,0:15:30.31,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,（コユキ）元気？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.33,0:15:36.06,Ragtime,,0,0,0,,Yeah...You look well too, Koyuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.39,0:15:36.52,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}元気[げんき]:lively/full of spirit|healthy
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.39,0:15:36.52,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,コユキも元気そうじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.77,0:15:46.44,Ragtime,,0,0,0,,I heard from Kayo-chan.\NYou sang with Dying Breed?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.86,0:15:44.24,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,（泉）カヨちゃんに聞いたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.36,0:15:46.53,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}ライブ:live (esp. concert, show, etc.)/live performance, 歌う[うたう]:to sing|to sing (one's praises in a poem, etc.)/to compose a poem
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.36,0:15:46.53,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,ダイブリのライブで\N歌ったんだってね
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.44,0:15:48.28,Ragtime,,0,0,0,,That's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.66,0:15:48.12,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}すごい:terrible/dreadful|amazing (e.g. of strength), じゃん:isn't it
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.66,0:15:48.12,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,すごいじゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.28,0:15:51.62,Ragtime,,0,0,0,,Yeah...Matt called me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.32,0:15:51.24,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}マット:mat, 誘う[さそう, いざなう]:to invite/to ask|to tempt
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.32,0:15:51.24,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,（コユキ）うん\Nマットが誘ってくれたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.58,0:15:54.83,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}背伸び[せのび]:standing on tiptoe and stretching one's back to make oneself taller/stretching oneself|overreaching oneself
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.58,0:15:54.83,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,（泉）ねえ コユキ…\N背伸びたんじゃない？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.62,0:15:54.45,Ragtime,,0,0,0,,Say, Koyuki...Haven't you grown a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.96,0:15:58.67,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}同じ[おなじ, おんなじ]:same/identical|(usu. part of a 'nara' conditional) anyway
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.96,0:15:58.67,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,（コユキ）あ 斎藤さんにも\N同じこと言われた
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.22,0:15:58.35,Ragtime,,0,0,0,,Saito-san said the same thing to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.25,0:16:02.26,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}大人[おとな, だいにん]:adult, 大人[たいじん]:man of substance or virtue|giant|adult, っぽい:-ish/-like|tossing something out
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.25,0:16:02.26,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,何か 大人っぽくなったね
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.29,0:16:01.88,Ragtime,,0,0,0,,You seem more grown up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.80,0:16:09.73,Ragtime,,0,0,0,,Hmm...Maybe it's because I'm being\Nforced to swim 3 kilometers every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.84,0:16:10.10,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}強いて[しいて]:by force, 毎日[まいにち]:every day
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.84,0:16:10.10,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,ん～ 強いて言えば\N毎日３キロは泳がされてますから
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.30,0:16:17.47,Ragtime,,0,0,0,,I see...I haven't swum\Nfor a while. I wish I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.35,0:16:13.85,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,そっか～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.77,0:16:17.35,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}久しぶり[ひさしぶり]:a long time (since the last time)/it's been a while (since I last saw, mailed, etc., you), 泳ぐ[およぐ]:to swim
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.77,0:16:17.35,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,私も久しぶりに泳ぎたいな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.47,0:16:20.14,Ragtime,,0,0,0,,But I haven't got a swimsuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.69,0:16:20.06,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}水着[みずぎ]:bathing suit/swimsuit/swimmers
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.69,0:16:20.06,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,でも水着ないんだよね～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.14,0:16:21.27,Ragtime,,0,0,0,,You don't swim?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.19,0:16:21.36,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}泳ぐ[およぐ]:to swim
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.19,0:16:21.36,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,（コユキ）泳がないの？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.98,0:16:25.48,Ragtime,,0,0,0,,Then tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.07,0:16:24.36,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}あした:morning, あした:tomorrow|near future
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.07,0:16:24.36,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,じゃ あした—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.48,0:16:27.54,Ragtime,,0,0,0,,Shall we go to buy me a swimsuit?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.61,0:16:27.61,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}水着[みずぎ]:bathing suit/swimsuit/swimmers, 買い[かい]:buying|buyer|purchase
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.61,0:16:27.61,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,水着買いに行こうか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.16,0:16:41.27,Ragtime,,0,0,450,,"Summer Sale"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.27,0:16:41.87,Ragtime,,0,0,450,,"Summer Sale"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.27,0:16:41.87,Ragtime,,0,0,0,,\NI wonder if it's a little too small.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.38,0:16:43.67,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}小さい[ちいさい]:small/little/tiny
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.38,0:16:43.67,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,（泉）ちょっと小さいかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.87,0:16:43.16,Ragtime,,0,0,0,,I wonder if it's a little too small.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.61,0:16:57.10,Ragtime,,0,0,0,,Well, it had been quite a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.72,0:16:57.48,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}ホント:truth/reality/actuality, 久しぶり[ひさしぶり]:a long time (since the last time)/it's been a while (since I last saw, mailed, etc., you)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.72,0:16:57.48,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,（コユキ）だって ホント…\N久しぶりだったから…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.31,0:17:01.40,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}変[へん]:strange|unexpected|change||
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.31,0:17:01.40,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,あ ごめん 何か変なこと言って…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.45,0:17:01.25,Ragtime,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry if I said\Nanything I shouldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.63,0:17:22.92,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}彼氏[かれし]:boyfriend, 別れる[わかれる]:to part (usu. of people)|to separate (of a couple)|to lose (e.g. one's mother)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.63,0:17:22.92,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,彼氏と別れたんだ…\N（コユキ）えっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.64,0:17:22.94,Ragtime,,0,0,0,,-I broke up with my boyfriend...\N-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.60,0:17:48.50,Ragtime,,0,0,0,,No more gloomy subjects.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.73,0:17:48.70,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}暗い[くらい]:dark|dark (in colour)|depressed||, 話題[わだい]:topic/subject, おしまい:the end/closing|That's it
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.73,0:17:48.70,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,（泉）暗い話題はおしまい！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.90,0:17:51.36,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,ん んん… ハァ～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.44,0:17:53.94,Ragtime,,0,0,0,,Say...Let's go swimming!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.49,0:17:53.87,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}泳ぐ[およぐ]:to swim
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.49,0:17:53.87,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,ねえ 泳ぎ行こ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.94,0:17:56.77,Ragtime,,0,0,0,,The public pool's closed today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.08,0:17:56.70,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}きょう:imperial capital (esp. Kyoto)|final word of an iroha-uta, きょう:bad luck/bad fortune|evil, 市営[しえい]:municipal management, プール:(swimming) pool, 休み[やすみ]:rest|vacation|dormancy (of a silkworm prior to moulting)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.08,0:17:56.70,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,きょうは市営プール 休みだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.11,0:18:06.78,Ragtime,,0,0,0,,Oh, Yukio...A girl named Maho's\Nbeen calling for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.21,0:18:06.21,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}真帆[まほ]:spread-out sail/full sail/(sailing) downwind, 何回[なんかい]:how many times?, 電話[でんわ]:telephone call/phone call|telephone (device)
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.21,0:18:06.21,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,（コユキの母）ああ 幸雄\N真帆って子から何回も電話あったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.78,0:18:11.15,Ragtime,,0,0,0,,What? If she calls again,\Ntell her I'll call her back later.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.88,0:18:08.84,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}かかる:to span/to bridge/to cross, かかる:to take (a resource, e.g. time or money)|to hang
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.88,0:18:08.84,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,（コユキ）え？\Nまたかかってきたら—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.97,0:18:11.68,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}かける:to hang (e.g. picture)/to hoist (e.g. sail)|to sit, かける:to run (race, esp. horse)/to dash|to gallop (one's horse)
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.97,0:18:11.68,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,あとで こっちからかけるって\N言っといて！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.47,0:18:19.48,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,（コユキ）\Nハァ… ハァ… ハァ…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.97,0:18:28.23,Ragtime,,0,0,0,,If you don't come, I'll go alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.98,0:18:28.74,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,（泉）コユキが来なくても\N私は１人で行ってるね
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.94,0:19:00.23,Ragtime,,0,0,0,,It's been a year since then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.97,0:19:00.18,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,あれから１年か…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.29,0:19:20.92,Ragtime,,0,0,0,,Izumi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.33,0:19:20.33,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy60}泉[いずみ]:spring/fountain
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.33,0:19:20.33,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,泉ちゃん！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.29,0:19:27.34,Default-jw,,0,0,0,,コユキ 来てくれたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.30,0:19:27.33,Ragtime,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're here, Koyuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.33,0:19:27.46,Ragtime,,250,0,150,,"School Facility-No Trespassing"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.33,0:19:27.46,Ragtime,,0,0,0,,\NOh, you're here, Koyuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.46,0:19:31.74,Ragtime,,250,0,150,,"School Facility-No Trespassing"
